| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-0690 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 277ae4cf-34ff-54e0-ba5c-1c6dea4c040f"
